  "title": "refactor(InstantSearch): avoid to store searchParameters",
  "body": "This PR removes the `searchParameters` from the `InstantSearch` instance. We don't have to keep track of the them because we already have access to them through the `helper.state`. The PR only removes the reference on the `InstantSearch` not the usage of the `searchParameters` option.",
